@startuml SD_Review

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #FFF8F0
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #CC6600
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF0D0

title SmartPOS+ — Sequence: Customer Review + BERT Sentiment

actor       "Customer"          as CU
participant "Shop.razor"        as SH
participant "ReviewService"     as RS
participant "BertApiClient"     as BERT
participant "AppDbContext"      as DB
participant "AuditService"      as AU

CU  -> SH   : Click "Leave a Review" on product
SH  -> DB   : Verify customer purchased this product\n(SaleItems JOIN Sales WHERE CustomerId = id)

alt Not purchased
  DB  --> SH  : No match
  SH  -> CU   : "You can only review products you have purchased."
else Purchased
  DB  --> SH  : Confirmed
  SH  -> CU   : Show review form (1-5 stars + comment)

  CU  -> SH   : Select rating + type comment
  CU  -> SH   : Click "Submit Review"
  SH  -> SH   : Validate rating (1-5), comment not empty

  SH  -> RS   : SubmitReview(customerId, productId, rating, comment)
  RS  -> DB   : INSERT Reviews (Rating, Comment, Sentiment=null, Score=null)
  DB  --> RS  : Review.Id

  RS  --> SH  : Saved
  SH  -> CU   : "Review submitted! Analysing sentiment..."

  RS  -> BERT : POST /analyse { text: comment }

  note right of BERT
    Positive  → score = 1.0
    Neutral   → score = 0.5
    Negative  → score = 0.0
  end note

  alt BERT unavailable
    BERT --> RS : timeout / 503
    RS   -> AU  : LogAction("Review submitted - sentiment pending", "Reviews")
    AU   -> DB  : INSERT AuditLogs
  else BERT responds
    BERT --> RS : { sentiment: "Positive", score: 0.92 }
    RS  -> DB   : UPDATE Reviews SET Sentiment="Positive", SentimentScore=0.92
    RS  -> AU   : LogAction("Review submitted - Positive", "Reviews")
    AU  -> DB   : INSERT AuditLogs
    RS  --> SH  : Sentiment result
    SH  -> CU   : Show sentiment badge (Positive)
  end
end

@enduml
